com.tractrac.model.lib.api.sensor

Interface ISensorData

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ITimeData

    public interface ISensorData
extends ITimeData
    This interface implements sensor data. It has some methods to retrieve custom dimensions and it also has methods to retrieve sensor data in a raw format
